    <item>
      <title>交易员们为漫长而动荡的选举之夜做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-03/how-traders-are-preparing-to-watch-2024-election-night-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着结果陆续公布，一些精神高度集中的投资者将密切关注利润率，并调整他们的赌注，直到日出为止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-03/how-traders-are-preparing-to-watch-2024-election-night-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 20:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从股票到加密货币，投资者为美国大选波动做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/investors-from-stocks-to-crypto-brace-for-us-election-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在竞争激烈、胜负难分的美国大选之前，各个市场的期权交易员似乎都在降低风险，准备迎接更多波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/investors-from-stocks-to-crypto-brace-for-us-election-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
